Quelle sera la sortie de ce code ?
<pre><code>def split_kwargs(**kwargs):
    nums = {k: v for k, v in kwargs.items() if isinstance(v, (int, float))}
    strs = {k: v for k, v in kwargs.items() if isinstance(v, str)}
    return nums, strs

print(split_kwargs(a=1, b="hello", c=2.0, d="world"))</code></pre>

Quelle est la sortie de ce code ?
<pre><code>def group_by_type(**kwargs):
    groups = {}
    for k, v in kwargs.items():
        t = type(v).__name__
        if t not in groups:
            groups[t] = {}
        groups[t][k] = v
    return groups

print(group_by_type(a=1, b="hello", c=2.0, d="world"))</code></pre>

Quelle sera la valeur de result ?
<pre><code>def apply_defaults(**kwargs):
    defaults = {"mode": "test", "retry": 3}
    for k, v in defaults.items():
        if isinstance(v, (int, float, str)):
            kwargs.setdefault(k, v)
    return kwargs

result = apply_defaults(mode="prod", timeout=30)</code></pre>

